(209, 1, '2015-09-29 21:37:30', '2015-09-30 04:37:30', '[rev_slider Slider1]\r\n\r\n[accordian divider_line="" class="faqtoggle" id="faqtoggle"]\r\n[toggle title=" Can I put my own logo on the wristbands?" open="no"]Yes you can. You can either upload it on our online ordering system, or email it at sales@wristbandcreation.com. Once you send it to us, we will let you know if we are able to place it on the wristbands.[/toggle]\r\n[toggle title="Can you make a specific color that I wanted?" open="no"]Yes, we have a list of a thousand different colors you can choose from using our Pantone Chart, where we use exact PMS color matching.[/toggle]\r\n[toggle title="Do you ship internationally?" open="no"]Yes, even if we are a U.S. based company, we also serve the international market. We serve countries such as Canada, United Kingdom, and Australia.[/toggle]\r\n[toggle title="How do I order my wristbands?" open="no"]You can either call us at (800) 403-8050 to speak with one of our customer representatives, or order online.[/toggle]\r\n[toggle title="What payment methods do you accept?" open="no"]We accept all major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, Discover, American Express), Paypal, Google Checkout, Checks, Money Orders, and Bank Wire Transfers.[/toggle]\r\n[toggle title="What is your Pricematch Guarantee?" open="no"]Our Pricematch Guarantee states that if you find a price lower than ours, call us so that we can beat it by 5%! We are proud to have the lowest prices in the industry.[/toggle]\r\n[toggle title=" Do you offer rush shipping?" open="no"]Yes, you can deliver the wristbands to your hands in as early as 6 days. Call us at (800) 403-8050 or order online.[/toggle]\r\n[toggle title="Can I request for some samples?" open="no"]Yes, we can send you some samples to show you the quality of rubber bracelet we produce. We charge a small fee of $3.99 to pay for shipping and handling. You can click here to order samples.[/toggle]\r\n[/accordian]', 'FAQs', '', 'inherit', 'closed'